WEBVTT

00:11:28.292 --> 00:11:32.377
while poor kids are continuously
having food and resources

00:11:32.401 --> 00:11:33.994
taken from their mouths.

00:11:34.750 --> 00:11:38.511
Governors, senators, mayors,
city council members --

00:11:38.535 --> 00:11:41.399
if we're going to call
public education public education,

00:11:41.423 --> 00:11:43.006
then it should be just that.

00:11:43.555 --> 00:11:46.538
Otherwise, we should
call it what it really is:

00:11:46.562 --> 00:11:48.127
poverty insurance.

00:11:49.211 --> 00:11:50.653
"Public education:

00:11:50.677 --> 00:11:53.765
keeping poor kids poor since 1954."

00:11:53.789 --> 00:11:55.241
(Laughter)

00:11:56.733 --> 00:12:01.831
If we really, as a country, believe
that education is the "great equalizer,"